parameters:
Stolge of Affection: Hey, it looks like we have more
comrades and things are going well.
Clea: Stolge-san, do you also have business in the cave?
Stolge of Affection: Hey, I have something to tell Melos.
Stolge of Affection: I'll go ahead.
Thief Nora: Um, you seemed a bit tense there.

Clea: It seems like there was a discovery in the previous
investigation.

Mage Relm: That sounds exciting! It would be amazing if we
find something useful for magical research!
Thief Nora: Wait, wasn't this place supposed to be a lake?
Hole-digging Melos: Hey there, you came at a good time!

Hole-digging Melos: You must be Relm from the Magic Academy!
I want you to see the great discovery in the back, please
come!

Mage Relm: Hehe~! It seems that the fame of the great genius
me is already resounding.
Mage Relm: Alright, let's go deeper!
Clea: Is this... some kind of ruins?

Melos: Ah, this is quite old. It might be from before the
birth of Fotizona.

Melos: This might actually be from the ancient kingdom of
Basileia, the oldest of all...!
Mage Relm: So, what do you intend to make this genius do?

Melos the Digger: I want you to take a look at this door.
It's clearly sealed with the power of magic.

Melos the Digger: If you're a mage from the academy, you
should be able to unlock it--

Mage Relm: Understood, but there is a condition! Please
allow me to be the first to search the interior.

Melos the Digger: I don't mind, but I have no idea what
could be inside.

Mage Relm: That's why we need a mage, right? Besides, there
are also people who can fight decently.

Clea: I have no problem with it. I'm also a little
interested.

Melos the Digger: I understand... but if you determine it's
dangerous, please come back immediately.

Stolge of Affection: Looks like the conversation has come to
a conclusion. I came here because I have something to
discuss with you, Melos.

Melos the Digger: I-I'm sorry! I apologize for the delay in
the report to the guild.

Stolge of Affection: Haaah, that doesn't matter, are you
properly returning home?

Stolge of Affection: No job should be a reason to leave a
frail girl alone, right?
Melos the Digger: I'm sorry... Stolge.
Stolge of Affection: Apologize to my daughter, not to me.

Stolge of Affection: Clea, there's a new request. Can you go
with this person and escort them to their house?

Stolge of Affection: Can you do me a favor even after
exploring here?
Mage Relm: Hmm... What is this...

Hole-digging Melos: H-How is it? Do you think we can unlock
it?
Mage Relm: Well, please take a look.

Mage Relm: Oh, this is the place of the abyss where the
demon sealed in the grimoire by the ancestor Subma resides.
Follow my words and unleash your power from the depths,
Akuri.
Mage Relm: Gate-opening demon, Somustan, open the door!
Clea: Amazing, this is the magic of gate-opening.

Mage Relm: This is the true power of a mage... huff...
puff... Did you understand?
Thief Nora: A-Are you okay? You don't look so good.

Mage Relm: N-No problem! It's just that it's been a while,
so I'm a little tired.

Mage Relm: If it's something like this, I can unlock
treasure chests and doors!
Mage Relm: Well, complex spells can be tough.

Hole-digging Melos: Please, let me take care of the
exploration in your place!

\CL Area Liberation\c[18]\CL Fotizona Region/Ancient Ruins
Dungeon\c[0]
Melos the Hole Digger: 'I'm glad you're back!'

Melos the Hole Digger: I heard about the discovery from
Relm-kun. I was surprised to find out that it was such a
remarkable ruin.
Clea: What should we do from now on?

Melos the Hole Digger: That's right... First, should we
report to the guild leader? Sorry to ask, but can you come
with me?

Melos the Hole Digger: If you determine that it is a
dangerous situation where you don't know what awaits, please
come back immediately.

Melos the Digger: Actually, I found a new ruins. I'll send a
request, so if you're interested, I'd like to ask you to
investigate it.
Melos the Digger: And also Ect...

Melos the Digger: I want you to play with Ect again. That
child really loves all of you, you know.

Relm: Please let me lead the investigation through this
door.
Will you enter the ancient ruins?
Clea (Let's prepare first before we do that)

events.name: 【058】試験官クレア 自動実行

parameters:
Girl Ect: Grr...!! I will definitely join the Adventurer's
Guild!

Stolge of Affection: Well, well, considering it's a recovery
from an illness, you're moving quite well.

Stolge of Affection: It seems like you can calmly assess
your own combat abilities, having taken down a few with
traps.

Clea: I feel like she has put in a lot of effort and is
determined to join the Adventurer's Guild.
Stolge of Affection: Like my past self, huh?
Clea: Yes, it's like I'm looking at my past self.

Clea: I'm going to help Ect. The opponent that appeared now
is tough for Ect.

Stolge of Affection (She assessed Ect's abilities and came
to help. I see... She has become more of an adventurer than
I thought.)

Stolge of Affection (That timid village girl from back then
has grown quite a lot...)

Stolge of Affection (I remember various things when I look
at them.)
Do you want to view Stolge of Affection's character episode?

Clea: I'll take care of the opponent here, so Ect, please
step back.
Young girl Ect: Thank you very much!

Clea: Don't worry, please consider the last one as an
exception.
Clea: Stolge-san, is something the matter?

Stolge of Affection: When you reach my age, you start
thinking about various things, you know.

Stolge of Affection: Next, let's head to the Rakio Ruins and
see Ect's area of expertise.
Clea: Kuh... Ect, please just run away!

Stolge of Affection: Well then, shall I become your
opponent? Both of you are very important to the guild, after
all.
Stolge of Affection: Guild work is often dangerous.

Stolge of Affection: Always be prepared in case something
happens.

Stolge of Affection: Prepare yourself with a strong
determination to never lose--
Stolge of Affection: Phew... That was quite ferocious.
Young girl Ect: Thank you very much for saving me!
Stolge of Affection: It seems Ect is uninjured.

Stolge of Affection: Clea, don't forget to recover your
stamina, okay?
Clea: I'm sorry for showing such a pathetic sight...

Stolge of Affection: Hm? What's wrong? You seem like you
have something else to say.

Clea: ...I'm sorry, but I thought Stolge-san had nothing to
do with battles.

Stolge of Affection: Well, both Agonia and Shimos are like
that, right? I'm maintaining balance by acting as the
negotiator.

Stolge of Affection: You still have room to grow, I'm
looking forward to it, you know?

Stolge of Affection: Next, let's head to the Rakio Ruins and
see Ect's area of expertise.
